# Normalize line endings: keep LF in the index regardless of platform
# checkout setting. Without this, files authored or copied on Windows /
# WSL with CRLF endings show up as modified even when their content
# hasn't changed, polluting `git status` and `git diff`. The git working
# tree still gets native line endings on checkout where appropriate.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files — Git autodetects most, but pinning these avoids any
# accidental newline rewriting if a future textual heuristic drifts.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.fmu binary
*.mat binary
*.whl binary
*.egg binary
